&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement AEM components, templates, dialogs, and workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write efficient and reusable code using Java, Sling, OSGi, and JCR APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and extend Sling models, servlets, filters, and schedulers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement HTL (Sightly) for component development and front-end integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with front-end developers to integrate HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript into AEM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure and optimize AEM Dispatcher caching for performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and consume RESTful/GraphQL APIs for integration with external systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Digital Asset Management (DAM) features like metadata schemas, renditions, and workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot, debug, and optimize AEM code and performance issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in code reviews, unit testing, and CI/CD pipeline deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
