&lt;h3&gt;The opportunity:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an &lt;strong&gt;Art Director&lt;/strong&gt; you will be one of the members of our Marketing Communication Team, and you will work in tandem with a Copywriter to develop original and impactful creative concepts that accurately answer the needs of a client brief and influence the behavior of their target audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for creating the entire visual world around these concepts and manage their execution through the required communication channels (Television, Print, Online, SM, BTL, branding etc.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
