&lt;li&gt;Continually raise the bar on creativity, designing fresh visuals and concepts that connect with the desired audience and drives action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce visual materials for a variety of channels in different formats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be always up to date on industry and art/design trends&lt;/li&gt;
